909
00:39:56,579 --> 00:39:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] da ovo potpuno nisi ti.

910
00:39:58,360 --> 00:40:00,699
[SPEAKER_00] I tako da rekla bi kad iz ljubavi

911
00:40:00,699 --> 00:40:01,659
