[SPEAKER_00] reakcija psiher.

965
00:41:28,059 --> 00:41:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam sad jedan brinut o sebi

966
00:41:29,699 --> 00:41:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] i to dijelo je jako opasno

967
00:41:31,239 --> 00:41:32,860
[SPEAKER_00] i onda je tijelo imalo svoju reakciju

968
