978
00:41:47,599 --> 00:41:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno, da.

979
00:41:48,260 --> 00:41:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] Da, i on kaže,

980
00:41:49,699 --> 00:41:50,719
