1034
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:18,260
[SPEAKER_01] ili petnest minuta šetnje,

1035
00:43:18,260 --> 00:43:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] ili,

1036
00:43:18,619 --> 00:43:19,719
[SPEAKER_01] ma bilo što,

1037
00:43:19,719 --> 00:43:20,780
[SPEAKER_01] da se samo protegnem

1038
00:43:20,780 --> 00:43:21,940
[SPEAKER_01] je opet bolje od ništa.

1039
00:43:22,199 --> 00:43:23,320
[SPEAKER_00] I to je jedan faktor

1040
00:43:23,320 --> 00:43:25,860
