[SPEAKER_00] svoj način promjene,

1047
00:43:32,599 --> 00:43:35,139
[SPEAKER_00] ili u mentoriranju ljudi,

1048
00:43:35,139 --> 00:43:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] to poimanje,

1049
00:43:36,139 --> 00:43:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] ono, sve ili ništa

1050
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:39,219
[SPEAKER_00] i kako ta promjena treba izgledati

1051
