1100
00:45:19,719 --> 00:45:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] a nekad će to biti čačkalica

1101
00:45:21,039 --> 00:45:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] koja će čisto eto ostaviti neki mali žar

1102
00:45:24,079 --> 00:45:25,099
[SPEAKER_01] da može nastaviti dalje.

1103
00:45:25,420 --> 00:45:28,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vrijedi samo nastaviti se kretati što kašiš.

1104
00:45:28,920 --> 00:45:31,800
[SPEAKER_01] Baš lijepa i motivirajuća priča Anđela

1105
00:45:31,800 --> 00:45:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] i vjerujem da ne samo s ovom pričom

1106
00:45:33,800 --> 00:45:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] oko težine, već generalno

1107
00:45:35,739 --> 00:45:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] za promjenu nekog načina razmišljenja

1108
00:45:37,460 --> 00:45:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] i uvoženja dobrih navika,

1109
00:45:38,980 --> 00:45:42,179
[SPEAKER_01] vraćanja discipline, tako da hvala ti na tome.

1110
00:45:42,179 --> 00:45:44,059
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala tebe. Rekla bih da je zapravo

1111
00:45:44,059 --> 00:45:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] ovo zajednički nazivnik

1112
00:45:45,659 --> 00:45:47,340
[SPEAKER_00] semu ovome jedna metanoa.

1113
00:45:47,340 --> 00:45:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] Srca, uma, tijela, duha, svakodnevice.

1114
00:45:52,119 --> 00:45:53,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ne zanimariti nijedan dio.

1115
00:45:54,380 --> 00:45:55,780
[SPEAKER_01] ima li neka poruka

1116
00:45:55,780 --> 00:45:57,800
[SPEAKER_01] koju želiš prenijeti našim ženama

1117
00:45:57,800 --> 00:45:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] koje nas prate, možda i muškarcima?

1118
00:45:59,619 --> 00:46:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ne nužno samo onima

1119
00:46:01,579 --> 00:46:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] koji se možda bore s prekomjernom tijelesnom težinom,

1120
00:46:04,280 --> 00:46:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] već i generalno ovim temama

1121
00:46:05,739 --> 00:46:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] koje smo pokrili.

1122
00:46:07,400 --> 00:46:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] Pa rekla bih, evo, nemoj sebi stat na putu

1123
00:46:09,900 --> 00:46:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] i za ono što ti se čini nemoguće,

1124
00:46:12,659 --> 00:46:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] evo, povjeri Bogu da ti da milost,

1125
00:46:15,000 --> 00:46:17,179
[SPEAKER_00] da na onaj put koji je dosjedan,

1126
00:46:17,179 --> 00:46:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] nesavršen, nekad padneš, nekad se ustaneš,

1127
00:46:20,559 --> 00:46:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali da, evo, da ne ostaneš sebi i dužan sebe.

1128
00:46:24,500 --> 00:46:25,820
[SPEAKER_01] Lijepo si to završila.

1129
00:46:25,820 --> 00:46:27,780
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti puno još jednom na dolasku

1130
00:46:27,780 --> 00:46:29,079
[SPEAKER_01] i nadam se da se opet čujemo,

1131
00:46:29,079 --> 00:46:30,780
[SPEAKER_01] vidimo u nekom podcastu.

1132
00:46:30,780 --> 00:46:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] Možda, radujem se.

1133
00:46:31,940 --> 00:46:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] Sretno dalje s tvojom disciplinom.

1134
00:46:33,440 --> 00:46:34,179
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti.

1135
00:46:34,179 --> 00:46:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala tebi.

1136
00:46:34,960 --> 00:46:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] Drage naše osnažene, osnaženi,

1137
00:46:37,500 --> 00:46:38,619
[SPEAKER_01] lijepo vas pozdravljamo

1138
00:46:38,619 --> 00:46:40,300
[SPEAKER_01] na naše sljedeće zanimljive teme.

